title: Technolites Episode 1-SKIDROW

Technolites is an action packed top down shooter with an epic animated
adventure, fully voice acted. The first game in the genre to allow you
to build your own ship, with dozens of unique parts and weapons

INSTALL NOTES

1. Unpack the release
2. Mount or burn image
3. Install
4. Copy the cracked content from the SKIDROW folder and into the main
install folder and overwrite
